    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>A Frost-Draugr is a centuries-old undead warrior, pulled from forgotten barrows by a southwest-pulling power. Encased in ancient corroded armour and rimmed with perpetual frost, it walks with terrible patience toward the nearest source of warmth.</p>",
      "director": "<p>Frost-Draugr are slow, powerful, and inevitable. They walk toward the nearest warm body and hit it until it stops being warm. Their Cold Aura punishes melee engagement—the smart play is ranged attacks and kiting. But the Grave-Wisps are designed to make kiting difficult.</p>",
